=Description=

"Innovation labs shake things up by bringing different agencies together to come up with creative solutions, driving the collaboration and experimentation that is often sorely lacking in the public service. However, these labs too often work in a vacuum.

To make it easier for people to connect and collaborate with labs, Apolitical has compiled a directory of transformative government, public sector and policy innovation labs from around the world."
